rows.label: qst720403_msg0001
rows.name: Welcome back, everyone!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0002
rows.name:
We brought the ingredients
you asked for. Go ahead
and check them.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0003
rows.name: Then let me just...

rows.label: qst720403_msg0004
rows.name:
Three Grimdark Crabs,
five portions of Feris Beastmeat...

rows.label: qst720403_msg0005
rows.name:
Three Lactonuts, and
seven measures of Weeping Flour...

rows.label: qst720403_msg0006
rows.name:
Huh? It looks like there's
more here than I asked for.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0007
rows.name:
It's a little something
extra for you, Ivan.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0008
rows.name:
It would be bad for morale
if our quartermaster got sick.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0009
rows.name:
Eat some real food and
keep up the good work.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0010
rows.name: A-A-A-Adel-samaaaa!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0011
rows.name:
I, Ivan, will serve you with all my
heart and soul until I can repay
this kindness, Adel-sama!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0012
rows.name: You're overdoing it.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0013
rows.name:
Adel-sama, if you don't mind,
could you let Sata and me
make today's meal?

rows.label: qst720403_msg0014
rows.name: You and Satahiko?

rows.label: qst720403_msg0015
rows.name: Mm-hm.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0016
rows.name:
With all the new people,
the cooks look overwhelmed,
so we'd like to help if we can.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0017
rows.name: That's wonderful.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0018
rows.name: Alright, I'm counting on you.

rows.label: qst720403_msg0019
rows.name: Right! Let's go, Sata!

rows.label: qst720403_msg0020
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] But this is just a temporary fix...

rows.label: qst720403_msg0021
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] I need to come up
with a real solution...
